Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.520
 Resort Caves Beach (adults only) 

00:00:03.120 --> 00:00:06.080
 Located in Hurghada, in the Al-Ahiya district, 17 km from the marina of New Marina 

00:00:06.680 --> 00:00:09.080
 It features an outdoor swimming pool, a private beach, barbecue facilities, a children's playground and a bar. 

00:00:09.780 --> 00:00:12.500
 All rooms are equipped with satellite TV, and some have a seating area. 

00:00:13.300 --> 00:00:16.220
 Some rooms have a terrace or balcony. 

00:00:16.860 --> 00:00:19.360
 The private bathroom includes a bath or shower, hairdryer and free toiletries. 

00:00:20.300 --> 00:00:22.960
 A 24-hour front desk, ATM, a gift shop and shops are at guests' disposal. 

00:00:23.880 --> 00:00:26.280
 The area is popular for snorkelling and windsurfing. 

00:00:27.060 --> 00:00:30.060
 Caves Beach Resort (adults only) is 23 km from Hurghada's Great Aquarium and 27 km from Senzo Shopping Center. 

00:00:32.360 --> 00:00:34.360
 Hurghada International Airport is 18 km away. 

